cdata.name: Abele
cdata.desc:
Abele is a digital assets bank that aims tobuild a digital financial infrastructure for the token economy, substituting theregular methods for digital assets storage (I.e. online and offline crypto-wallets). Abele users will be able to safeguard theirdigital assets within the platforms digital custodial service, in an institutional manner.

The ABELE token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency developed by the Abele group. It is asecurity token and provides access to the Abeleplatform products and services.
